    "body": "I just wanted to add that there is a workaround for this issue, but it looks rather ugly:\r\n\r\n```python\r\ndf = df.stack('metrics').to_frame().unstack('dim2')\r\ndf.columns = df.columns.droplevel()\r\nprint(df)\r\n\r\ndim2          A   B\r\ndim1 metrics       \r\nDIM  c        1  11\r\n     b        2  22\r\n     a        3  33\r\n     d        4  44\r\n```\r\n\r\nAs you can see it produces one of the expected outputs mentioned above."
